sentences: Fernando (born 12 December 1976 in Oviedo, Spain) is a member of the Asturian power metal band WarCry.
When he was eight years old, he was interested in the keyboard and the flute.
Two years later he began studying music theory, rhythm, piano and organ.
He was 17 years old and he was competent on the keyboard.
In 2001 he was fired from Avalanch, along with Alberto Ardines.
Since 2002 he has worked on all the band's albums.
On 25 August 2007 he participated in his last concert with WarCry.
Four days later he decided to leave the band, along with Alberto Ardines.
